node.accessibility_caption: Photo by MINDSET THERAPY™ on August 15, 2021. May be an image of text that says '28 Life Lessons Worth Sharing 1) No one has it all figured out 2) Being nice is overrated, be kind, be fair be understanding not "nice" 3) Το love is to be vulnerable let your guard down 4) Good or bad, you can learn from everybody read via twitter @CJ Johnson17th MINDSET THERAPY'.

Photo by MINDSET THERAPY™ on August 15, 2021. May be an image of text that says '5) Embrace all of your emotions, don't ignore them, don't mask them embrace them 6) Traveling alone is better than with bad company 7) Unlearning is just as important as learning read via twitter /@CJ_ Johnson17th MINDSET THERAPY'.

Photo by MINDSET THERAPY™ on August 15, 2021. May be an image of text that says '8) No one prepares you to watch your parents grow old olo 9) Own up to your mistakes /Do what you say you'll do 10) Maturity is accepting you won't get answers to the shit that hurt you the most, heal anyway read via twitter @CJ Johnson17th MINDSET THERAPY'.

Photo by MINDSET THERAPY™ on August 15, 2021. May be an image of text that says '11) One of the most important decisions you'll ever make in life, is who you have children with. Choose wisely 12 Women friends are cool, don't try to sleep with them 13 You don't have to learn everything the hard way via twitter @CJ Johnson17th MINDSET THERAPY'.

Photo by MINDSET THERAPY™ on August 15, 2021. May be an image of text that says '14) One day you'll need to be forgiven so learn to forgive others 15) Instead of buying your children what you didn't have, teach them what you didn't know 16) Never let your inner child die read via twitter @CJ Johnson17th MINDSET THERAPY'.

Photo by MINDSET THERAPY™ on August 15, 2021. May be an image of text that says '17) If someone doesn't treat you as good as a chick fil a employee they don't deserve to be in your life 18) No one reads mind, speak on how you feel 19) Never feel bad about promoting yourself read via twitter @CJ Johnson17th MINDSET THERAPY'.

Photo by MINDSET THERAPY™ on August 15, 2021. May be an image of text that says '20) If you value your time say no to anything that you don't absolutely want to do 21) Spending time alone is one of the best things you can do 22) Celebrate your accomplishments read via twitter @CJ Johnson17th MINDSET THERAPY'.

Photo by MINDSET THERAPY™ on August 15, 2021. May be an image of text that says '23) If you care too much about what other people think, you're effectively their slave 24) Be so busy improving your life that you don't have time to criticize others 25) Everyone you love will eventually die, spend your time with your loved ones, keep them close Thread via twitter @CJ Johnson17th MINDSET THERAPY'.

Photo by MINDSET THERAPY™ on August 15, 2021. May be an image of text that says '26) Lister to understand, not to respond 27) Hang out with people from different races, ethnicities and social economic classes 28) You can't pour from an empty cup, take care of yourself first Thread Threadvatwtter/@CJ_Johnsonf7th via twitter @CJ Johnson17th MINDSET THERAPY'.

Photo by MINDSET THERAPY™ on August 15, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Believe in your heart and soul that you are capable of big things in your life. The only thing that is standing in your way is yourself. Remove your glass ceiling. Type YES if you agree. MINDSET THERAPY'.
